2.1.0.name: wordpress/angler
2.1.0.description: Angler is a highly customizable but simple theme. It's a two column theme with fixed-width and widget-ready. Angler is our first of our series of SEO optimized wordpress themes. You have a couple of options in the admin panel.  You can easily change the color scheme. You can choose if (and where) you want to use thumbnails or not.  You can hide or show posts meta data.
